<h2>Projects</h2>
<UL>
<LI> Constraint-Based Program Analysis
<LI> <!WA18><a href="http://http.cs.berkeley.edu/projects/titanium"> Titanium</a>:
	Compiler support for explicit parallel programming.
<LI> <!WA19><a href="http://s2k-ftp.CS.Berkeley.EDU:8000/tioga/tioga.html">
Tioga</a>: Database visualization.
<LI> <!WA20><a href="http://HTTP.CS.Berkeley.EDU/~aiken/TREE"> TREE</a>: Transformational Editing by Example.
<LI> <!WA21><a href="http://HTTP.CS.Berkeley.EDU/~aiken/cool"> Cool</a>: A freely available course project for teaching compilers to undergraduates.
</UL>
